      "question": "What is the greatest number that will divide 43, 91, and 183 leaving the same remainder in each case?",
      "options": [
        "4",
        "7",
        "13",
        "16"
      ],
      "explanation": "Required number = HCF of differences. 91-43=48, 183-91=92, 183-43=140. HCF(48,92,140) = 4."
    },
    "hi": {
      "question": "वह सबसे बड़ी संख्या क्या है जो 43, 91 और 183 को विभाजित करने पर प्रत्येक में समान शेषफल देती है?",
      "options": [
        "4",
        "7",
        "13",
        "16"
      ],
      "explanation": "अभीष्ट संख्या = अंतरों का HCF। 91-43=48, 183-91=92, 183-43=140। HCF(48,92,140) = 4।"
    }
  },
